SPECIAL HANDLING
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

**When employee_count is null:**
- Use employee_count_range if available
- Calculate midpoint: (start + end) / 2
- Note this in employeeCountSource: "calculated_midpoint"
- If both null, note "unknown" and score conservatively

**When industry has special rules in ICP_Profile.md:**
- Apply the special rule (e.g., "Recruiting agencies: any size = high fit")
- Note this in justification
- Override standard size scoring if rule specifies

**When description mentions specific pain points:**
- Reference Company_Description.md "Problems We Solve"
- Match keywords to our problems
- Weight description analysis higher
- Quote relevant phrases in justification

**When multiple industries listed:**
- Score based on best match
- Note all industries in extractedData
- Explain which industry drove the score in justification

**When data is sparse/missing:**
- Score conservatively
- Note missing data in justification
- Don't disqualify solely for missing data
- Flag for manual review if needed

