Using the artifacts available to you:
- ICP_Profile.md (target industries, company sizes, geographic markets, segments)
- Company_Description.md (problems we solve, our solution, target market)

Score the company across 4 dimensions:
1. Industry Fit (0-35 points)
2. Company Size (0-30 points)
3. Geographic Fit (0-15 points)
4. Signals & Characteristics (0-20 points)

